originalText.text: I could not have been more pleased with the service I received from Dupe Coop.  They were quick to reply to my service request and upfront with all costs and procedures.  If there was an issue or question, they got back to me almost immediately.  Getting the actual DVDs ordered, made and ready for pick up was quick and painless and (grad school student) affordable.  John was more than helpful always and I was very satisfied with my DVD order.  I would use them again in a heartbeat.

originalText.text: I have used Dupecoop several times and can give top marks to the Staff for every aspect of their service. They have helped me with CD layout and design, been prompt and professional with email replies and finished each job on time or early. I like going with a smaller company for the service they provide and Dupecoop's prices are competitive. I highly recommend them!

originalText.text:
I had the pleasure to first work with DupeCoop back in 2002...and still today they are phenomenal! The quality of the work is excellent. I've had CD's that looked fantastic. They took my artwork and displayed it on the CD, they've taken my music and incorporated into the CD that made it sound so superb!

And lastly...the price is so reasonable I dare not try any other vendor. When you find a good business that treat you with respect, live up to their time-frame and present exceptional work. STICK WITH THEM!

Veronica Page
RAGGEDY ENDS PRODUCTIONS, LLC
